 60px;\">[/restrict]</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[restrict role=\"subscriber\" ] <strong><span style=\"color: #333333;\">This  Content is restricted to Subscriber Only </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[/restrict]</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[restrict role=\"contributor\" ] <span style=\"color: #000000;\">T<strong>his  Content is restricted to Contributor Only</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[/restrict]</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[restrict level=\"youngsters\" ] <span style=\"color: #000000;\">T<strong>his  Content is restricted to Youngsters Only</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 60px;\">[/restrict]</p>\r\nContent can be restricted either by role or access-level.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Article Content Restriction','','publish','open','open','','content-restriction-example','','','2018-03-13 01:45:06','2018-03-13 09:45:06','',0,'http://96.67.213.65/?p=155',0,'post','',0),(158,10,'2018-03-12 22:21:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2018-03-12 22:21:22','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://96.67.213.65?p=158&preview=true&preview_id=158',0,'post','',0),(159,6,'2018-03-12 22:22:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2018-03-12 22:22:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://96.67.213.65?p=159&preview=true&preview_id=159',0,'post','',0),(160,2,'2018-03-12 22:39:11','2018-03-13 06:39:11','','a2_1','','inherit','open','closed','','a2_1','','','2018-03-13 01:49:26','2018-03-13 09:49:26','',20,'http://96.67.213.65/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/a2_1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(161,2,'2018-03-12 22:39:12','2018-03-13 06:39:12','','a2_2','','inherit','open','closed','','a2_2','','','2018-03-13 02:47:10','2018-03-13 10:47:10','',205,'http://96.67.213.65/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/a2_2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(162,2,'2018-03-12 22:39:12','2018-03-13 06:39:12